Package index

API data

All functions that start with get_ and track_ are used to download data via API.

get_code()
Get the codes of geographical levels
get_change()
Get geo code changes with API
get_correspond()
Get geo corresponds
track_change()
Track all changes for codes from API
track_split()
Get geo code that are split after code change
track_merge()
Get geo code that are merged after code change

Geographical levels

Codes with different geograhical levels for a specific year

cast_geo()
Cast geo granularity from API
